detaileddescription.para:
Returns a lazily initialized value of the operation attribute. Initialized once and only once and stored for subsequent access with proper synchronization. In case of any exception or error thrown by the lazy value initializer, the result will not be memoised (i.e. remembered) and on next call computation will be attempted again.
A lazily initialized value of theoperation attribute
